h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click *Agent* sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Agent Currency Posting* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Agent Currency Posting"|guide:ShowExhAgentCurrencyPostingActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* [Open "Agent Currency Posting" in Edit Mode|guide:SelectExhAgentCurrencyPostingActionService].
* User must enter valid input to update.
* Click "Update" button.
* Update *Agent Currency Posting*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Update Agent Currency Posting" privilege.
* Follow rules of validation:
{table}
*Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Rules*
[Agent|guide:ExhAgentDropDownTagLib] | Drop Down List | Numeric | Required
Amount | Text Box | Alpha Numeric | Required
{table}

* Match expected version before updating a *Agent Currency Posting*.

h4. Process:
* Update selected *Agent Currency Posting*.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Update selected *Agent Currency Posting* into grid-view.
** Show success message.
** Reset the field for next inputs.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

